We idle and occasionally talk at: irc.freenode.net #rubberfuse

= Mailinglist =
Users can subscribe to our list by sending an email to
rubberhose-request@freelists.org with 'subscribe' in the Subject field OR by
visiting our list page at http://www.freelists.org/list/rubberhose

= Things we need to investigate =

* What are recent advances in filesystem and storage technology which could benefit this project?
* Find out if certain security measures in Rubberhose are outdated and see if we can add new ones.

